Package: CRBHits
Title: Conditional reciprocal best hits (CRBHit) in R
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Kristian K",
           family = "Ullrich",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "ullrich@evolbio.mpg.de",
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-4308-9626"))
Maintainer: Kristian K Ullrich <ullrich@evolbio.mpg.de>
Description: CRBHits calculates conditional reciprocal best hit (CRBHit) pairs and subsequently can classify tandem duplicates, assign syntney groups and calculate Ka/Ks values.
